{"tid":910194,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人因為怕醜、怕樣衰而錯過左好多機會?","createTime":"2018-11-21T03:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T17:18:19.000Z","uid":65220,"like":118,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b072a33239ecd10ef2cc1d10d96cc423bd2e6565","tid":910194,"uid":65220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T03:46:06.000Z","msg":"好深刻<br />\n以前幼稚園去交通安全城, 有印象可以簡做駕駛者、過天橋、路人<br />\n咁扮駕駛者同過天橋既小朋友得幾個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老師<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n<br />\n老師: 有無同學仔想試下做駕駛者? (者係踩單車)<br />\n我: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (想玩但唔敢舉手, 其他同學瞬間舉手, 名額已滿) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老師: 有無同學仔想試下去行天橋架? <br />\n我: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (玩唔到駕駛者, 想玩下過天橋但都係唔敢舉手, 其他同學瞬間舉手, 名額已滿) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最後只可以做路人甲  跟大隊過馬路就完左<br />\n<br />\nBTW 其實呢樣都係小事, 小學中學都一樣<br />\n想參加野又怕麻煩 <br />\n一係又怕自己應付唔到 從來唔會主動話要做<br />\n但其實心入面好想試下 <br />\n<br />\n到宜家都努力學緊 主動少少 出下聲 為自己爭取多啲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   有無巴絲都係咁<br />\n想聽下大家經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad1048e585249ad3a27eb9a99962e2b116fcbe2","tid":910194,"uid":199016,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T03:48:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5e65b47024812471d2bd07e0aae4aec22d79b02","tid":910194,"uid":129660,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T03:49:01.000Z","msg":"我唔係怕<br />\n而係因為樣衰，醜而錯失好多機會"},{"pid":"2b5624de0030cb1b20546c84e873fe2b1280ed25","tid":910194,"uid":177866,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T03:55:05.000Z","msg":"有時真係唔知驚乜春 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a83bef9da16d57eef880c9d82ce5bd12fa3a6f","tid":910194,"uid":100766,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T04:14:32.000Z","msg":"其實你冇做錯<br />\n因為我都係咁嘅人<br />\n但當你第一個舉手做咗嗰樣野<br />\n唔知點解個結果多數都係會柒<br />\n之後就會秒速後悔點解要衝出黎<br />\n久而久之我寧願縮返埋算"},{"pid":"0cf2337ef220bc1798bb5f1c357220df320b914c","tid":910194,"uid":101169,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T04:26:08.000Z","msg":"我反而因為真係樣衰而錯過好多機會<br />\n成日諗住我咁樣衰，冇人想見到我，不如自摺算數<br />\n<br />\n呢個活動要面試？不了，面試官見到我都唔開胃<br />\n出國交流？不了，冇人想同柒頭交流<br />\n識fd子活動？不了，靚仔專屬福利<br />\n拎scholarship？不了，我生得咁柒有乜資格申請<br />\n<br />\n根本上生得靚仔，冇可能錯過機會<br />\n你唔想去，老師同學都會鼓勵你去<br />\n久而久之啲機會自己會黎，人生都容易成功"},{"pid":"b1008244a388f62636a6141ed9c547df93ae9c3f","tid":910194,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T04:33:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a81d352c6109401cd477b9779b9e38da5d1a8b06","tid":910194,"uid":82542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T04:35:24.000Z","msg":"屌 咁撚似我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31809cb7a59386b75a89979fc1447250ed96e7ac","tid":910194,"uid":65220,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2b5624de0030cb1b20546c84e873fe2b1280ed25","tid":910194,"uid":177866,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T03:55:05.000Z","msg":"有時真係唔知驚乜春 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T08:14:04.000Z","msg":"同意呀 <br />\n其實唔知驚咩 怕比人望 唔知人地點諗自己掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68e3335b19c9756e3f3b0840426f570